story.text: Love the deer here. Love the mountains. Love our hill. Love this house.
Want to check air quality - so hard to breathe sometimes - I guess that is 5,000 feet for you.
Working from home today - loving my Great Falls matter, but it sucks that Tom is away for so long - need to get things moving.
Need to get someone to help me clean and moving on the deck.
